# CODEOWNERS
# Automatically requested as reviewers when a PR touches these paths.
# Format: <path-pattern> @<owner>
# Docs: https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositorys-settings-and-features/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners

# Global fallback — shifulegend reviews everything by default
*                   @shifulegend

# AI instruction and memory files — always reviewed by repo owner
docs/ai/**          @shifulegend
.github/copilot-instructions.md  @shifulegend
CLAUDE.md           @shifulegend
AGENTS.md           @shifulegend
gemini/GEMINI.md    @shifulegend

# Security-sensitive areas
.github/workflows/**  @shifulegend
**/config/**          @shifulegend
**/*.env*             @shifulegend
